### If Blythe Trust reaches 5:

Blythe shares his communication codes with ALICE:
> **Blythe:** "The watch frequencies are: 7.7.3.2. My authentication phrase is 'The ravens have left the Tower.' If you can reach them... tell them BLUE. Tell them I'm alive. Tell them..."

*He pauses.*

> **Blythe:** "Tell them to bring the large-animal kit. Just in case."

