- Nuclear reactor (OVERDRIVE state)
- ARCHIMEDES satellite (FOCUS/BROADCAST state)

AUTOMATIC FAILSAFE ENGAGED: Energy discharge required within 90 seconds.

Default target: LAIR_SELF_TARGET (Scorched Earth Protocol)

To select alternative target: Access ARCHIMEDES targeting interface.
Authorized users: DIRECTOR (Level 5)

Time remaining: 89... 88... 87...
```

